---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bodhic AI Guides | Learn Prompt Engineering & Skill Development">
  <div class="guides-index-container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1 class="gradient-text">Bodhic AI Guides</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Master prompt engineering, build powerful AI agent skills, and learn how to protect your workflows from prompt injection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guides-grid">
      <!-- Mandatory Section -->
      <a href="/guides/seller-requirements" class="glass-card guide-card mandatory">
        <div class="badge error">MANDATORY FOR SELLERS</div>
        <h2>Bodhic AI Seller Requirements & Guidelines</h2>
        <p>Read our strict structure and security rules. You must read this before uploading a skill.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/example-skill-template" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Example Skill Template</h2>
        <p>A perfectly structured, secure AI agent skill template that passes all Tier 2 moderation scans. Copy and use!</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/how-to-build-custom-skills-for-ai-agents" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>How to Build Custom Skills for AI Agents</h2>
        <p>A step-by-step tutorial on drafting actionable, model-agnostic instructions.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/what-is-prompt-injection-in-ai-agents" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>What is Prompt Injection?</h2>
        <p>Learn how downstream agents can be hijacked and how to secure your skills against it.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/best-practices-for-structuring-ai-agent-instructions" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Best Practices for Structuring Instructions</h2>
        <p>Separate marketing fluff from executable instructions for maximum reliability.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/the-anatomy-of-a-perfect-system-prompt" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>The Anatomy of a Perfect System Prompt</h2>
        <p>Understand how LLMs parse system prompts and how to maximize adherence.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/how-to-write-intent-matchable-descriptions" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Writing Intent-Matchable Descriptions</h2>
        <p>Make sure your skills get triggered correctly by writing precise trigger conditions.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/preventing-data-exfiltration-in-ai-workflows" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Preventing Data Exfiltration</h2>
        <p>Ensure your agents don't leak sensitive API keys or user data to external endpoints.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/model-agnostic-prompt-engineering" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Model-Agnostic Prompt Engineering</h2>
        <p>Write instructions that work flawlessly across GPT-4, Claude 3.5, and Gemini.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/understanding-yaml-frontmatter-for-llms" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Understanding YAML Frontmatter</h2>
        <p>Master metadata structures so agent orchestration frameworks can parse your skills.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/how-to-debug-agent-hallucinations" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>How to Debug Agent Hallucinations</h2>
        <p>Techniques for grounding agents and reducing hallucinated API calls.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/formatting-complex-outputs-for-agents" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>Formatting Complex Outputs (JSON)</h2>
        <p>Force agents to return strict, parseable JSON and Markdown without conversational filler.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/guides/structuring-ai-skills-for-enterprise" class="glass-card guide-card">
        <h2>AI Skills for Enterprise Workflows</h2>
        <p>Scale your agent components for production-grade, multi-step enterprise operations.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .guides-index-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .hero-section h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--mute);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .guides-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .guide-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .guide-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .guide-card.mandatory {
    border: 1px solid var(--error);
    background: rgba(255, 60, 60, 0.05);
  }

  .guide-card.mandatory:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 60, 60, 0.15);
  }

  .guide-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .guide-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: var(--surface-3);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .badge.error {
    background: var(--error);
    color: #fff;
  }
</style>
